cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper focuses on resource management in mobile edge computing systems, which involves networking, machine learning, and distributed systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a reinforcement learning-based algorithm, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with energy harvesting and renewable energy, which could be classified under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper uses simulations to validate the proposed algorithm, which could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
